overview: Dámaris gives her testimony and an energetic performance of these favorites with a live 40 piece orchestra and 150 voice choir.  Songs:  At The Name of Jesus  No, Not One  He is the Answer  Christ In Me  In the Presence of Jehovah  Is There Anything Too Hard For the Lord  He Has Forgiven Me  Giving My Life Away  He’s Been Faithful  I Am Not Ashamed of the Gospel
title: Dámaris Live, Not Ashamed
